sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Dashboard
    participant ElectionsAPI
    participant SupabaseDB
    participant KVStore
    
    alt Search by Code
        User->>Dashboard: Enter election code
        Dashboard->>ElectionsAPI: GET /api/elections?code=ABC1234
        ElectionsAPI->>SupabaseDB: Query by code
        SupabaseDB-->>ElectionsAPI: Election (if found)
        ElectionsAPI-->>Dashboard: Election or empty array
        Dashboard->>User: Navigate to election or show error
    else Get User's Elections
        User->>Dashboard: View dashboard
        Dashboard->>ElectionsAPI: GET /api/elections (with auth token)
        ElectionsAPI->>ElectionsAPI: Authenticate user
        ElectionsAPI->>SupabaseDB: Query by creator_id
        SupabaseDB-->>ElectionsAPI: Elections created by user
        ElectionsAPI-->>Dashboard: Elections array
        Dashboard->>User: Display elections list
    end

